      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. So you're saying the race itself helps establish that \"street credibility\" vibe. Let's try another archetype then. I have a character who is a \"brilliant, cold-blooded tech genius\"—maybe a CEO or a high-level consultant who is incredibly calculating, sophisticated, and operates in these very elite, high-society circles. What kind of physical look and racial background would you suggest to make this character feel most believable to viewers?",
